These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-1::.
There 7 different types of food: kiwi, eggplant, pepper, peach, onion, pear, carrot
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: blues, classical, jazz, r&b, reggae, rock, soul
The people have 7 different hobbies: magic-tricks, fishing, woodworking, traveling, singing, drawing, chess
 1. the person eating onion is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
 3. the person who's hobby is chess is between the fan of classical and the fan of blues##2
 4. the person eating peach is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 5. the fan of classical is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
 6. the person eating kiwi is the person who's hobby is chess##1
 7. the fan of r&b is between the person who's hobby is traveling and the person eating onion##2
 8. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 9. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
10. the person eating carrot is the fan of jazz##1
11. the fan of rock is the person eating peach##1
12. the person eating carrot is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
13. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the fan of reggae##1
14. the person eating pear is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person who's hobby is chess##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |    7     |
| Food   | onion | kiwi     | pear | eggplant | peach | carrot  | pepper  |
| Music-Genre   | blues  | r&b        | classical  | soul     | rock   | jazz       | reggae   |
| Hobby         | fishing   | chess | traveling    | woodworking  | singing | drawing | magic-tricks |

