.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-2::.
There 7 different types of food: orange, asparagus, peas, kale, spinach, lime, pineapple
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: punk, hip-hop, techno, country, indie, r&b, ambient
The people use 7 different means of transport: bus, car, roller, scooter, ship, train, trike
 1. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 2. the fan of indie is the fan of indie##1
 3. the fan of indie is on the right of the fan of country##1
 4. the fan of country is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 5. the fan of punk is the person eating pineapple##1
 6. the person eating orange is the person driving the scooter##1
 7. the person eating orange is between the fan of ambient and the person driving the trike##2
 8. the fan of techno is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
 9. the fan of ambient is on the left of the fan of country##1
10. the person eating peas is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
11. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person eating orange##1
12. the person driving the bus is the person eating asparagus##1
13. the person eating kale is on the left of the person eating orange##1
14. the person eating kale is on the right of the person driving the train##1
15. the person eating asparagus is on the far right##1
16. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3       |    4     |   5    |     6     |    7     |
| Food   | lime | pineapple      | kale     | orange  | spinach | peas | asparagus |
| Music-Genre         | hip-hop  | punk | r&b | techno | ambient | country   | indie  |
| Transport     | roller   | train     | trike        | scooter  | ship   | car       | bus      |

