.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-3::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, dunhill, dannemann, bluemaster, game, baccarat, montecristo
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: family, spy, adventure, martial-arts, zombie, scientific, thriller
The people use 7 different means of transport: helicopter, roller, scooter, snowmobile, taxi, trike, van
 1. the person driving the roller is the person watching family movies##1
 2. the person driving the taxi is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
 4. the person driving the scooter is the dunhill-smoker##1
 5. the person driving the trike is between the person driving the van and the person watching thriller movies##2
 6. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
 7. the game-smoker is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
 8. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
 9. the person driving the van is on the far right##1
10. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
11. the person driving the roller is the person watching family movies##1
12. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
13. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
14. the person driving the van is the montecristo-smoker##1
15. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the game-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |      5       |    6     |    7     |
| Cigar    | chaman     | game   | baccarat        | dunhill   | dannemann     | bluemaster     | montecristo    |
| Movie-Genre         | spy    | martial-arts | family | zombie | thriller | scientific | adventure |
| Transport   | helicopter | taxi       | roller     | scooter | snowmobile   | trike    | van      |

