 4. the person watching adventure movies is on the far right##1
 5. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
 6. the fonseca-smoker is on the far right##1
 7. the bongani-smoker is in the middle##1
 8. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the person who growsazalea is the person watching action movies##1
10. the person who growsdahlia is the baccarat-smoker##1
11. the person watching animation movies is the person who growsbegonia##1
12. the davidoff-smoker is the person who growsdaisy##1
13. the person who growsmarigold is on the far right##1
14. the person watching zombie movies is between the person watching animation movies and the person watching drama movies##2
