There are 7 different nationalities: australian, chinese, colombian, french, indian, japanese, malaysian
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: western, epic, family, documentary, musical, comedy, scientific
 1. the malaysian is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 2. the person eating banana is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
 3. the person eating banana is the chinese##1
 4. the person eating peas is the person watching documentary movies##1
 5. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 6. the australian is the person eating nectarine##1
 7. the person eating potato is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
 8. the person watching epic movies is the person eating raspberry##1
 9. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
10. the person watching comedy movies is the australian##1
11. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person eating peas##1
12. the person watching musical movies is between the person eating raspberry and the person eating potato##2
13. the colombian is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
14. the person watching western movies is the indian##1
15. the person eating banana is on the left of the australian##1
16. the person watching documentary movies is the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |     5      |     6      |     7     |
