 1. the cottage house is on the left of the security-guard##1
 2. the security-guard is on the left of the social-worker##1
 3. the wooden house is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 4. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the chef##1
 5. the librarian is the victorian house##1
 6. the art-deco house is between the dancer and the social-worker##2
 7. the chef is in the middle##1
 8. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the modern house##1
 9. the modern house is the person watching sports movies##1
10. the victorian house is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
11. the analyst is the townhouse house##1
12. the analyst is the townhouse house##1
13. the cottage house is on the right of the chef##1
14. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
15. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the librarian##1

.:: Answer ::.
