 1. the person eating strawberry is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's sport is volleyball is in the middle##1
 3. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
 4. the person eating radish is between the person eating cherry and the person eating grapes##2
 5. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 6. the person eating nectarine is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 7. the person eating cherry is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 8. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
 9. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
10. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
11. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
12. the person who growsbegonia is in the middle##1
13. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
14. the person who's sport is badminton is the person who growsdaisy##1
15. the person eating radish is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1

.:: Answer ::.
