.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-8::.
There 7 different types of food: apple, eggplant, garlic, orange, papaya, peas, pineapple
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: june, september, july, february, march, august, january
There are 7 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, sprite, 7up, hot-chocolate, cola, lemonade, water
 1. the person who's birthday is in february is in the middle##1
 2. the person eating pineapple is the person who's birthday is in july##1
 3. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person eating apple##1
 5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 6. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking water##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
 8. the person eating papaya is the person drinking soy-milk##1
 9. the person drinking lemonade is between the person eating pineapple and the person eating peas##2
10. the person who's birthday is in june is the person eating eggplant##1
11. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
12. the person drinking 7up is the person who's birthday is in september##1
13. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
14. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3     |      4      |     5      |      6      |    7    |
| Food    | peas   | orange  | pineapple | garlic      | eggplant   | papaya      | apple   |
| Birthday   | march | january | july   | february  | june | august | september |
| Beverage     | water | lemonade | sprite     | cola | hot-chocolate     | soy-milk        | 7up  |

