 4. the person who's birthday is in november is the person drinking juice##1
 5. the fan of soul is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 6. the person drinking fanta is the fan of trance##1
 7. the fan of jazz is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 8. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in december is the fan of gospel##1
10. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
11. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
12. the fan of trance is the person who's birthday is in may##1
13. the person who's birthday is in february is in the middle##1
14. the person who's birthday is in may is between the person drinking coffee and the person who's birthday is in november##2
15. the fan of funk is on the right of the fan of trance##1
