House: futuristic, modern, victorian, ranch-style, colonial, tower, palace
 1. the victorian house is the owner of the rat##1
 2. the owner of the cat is in the middle##1
 3. the owner of the hamster is on the far left##1
 4. the owner of the mouse is the colonial house##1
 5. the colonial house is on the right of the palace house##1
 6. the modern house is the owner of the cat##1
 7. the owner of the rat is the victorian house##1
 8. the turkish is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
 9. the tower house is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
10. the thai is on the right of the tower house##1
11. the victorian house is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
12. the ranch-style house is on the left of the russian##1
13. the palace house is on the left of the pakistani##1
14. the dutch is on the left of the malaysian##1
15. the owner of the rabbit is between the futuristic house and the thai##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2    |     3      |      4      |      5      |    6     |   7    |
| Nationality       | dutch | malaysian | thai     | russian | turkish | american  | pakistani |
