.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-16::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  coach, dancer, fisherman, manager, musician, photographer, writer
The people use 7 different means of transport: car, bus, ship, jet-ski, subway, tram, trike
House: victorian, ranch-style, futuristic, tower, palace, craftsman, art-deco
 1. the craftsman house is on the left of the fisherman##1
 2. the craftsman house is between the person driving the subway and the person driving the ship##2
 3. the person driving the car is the ranch-style house##1
 4. the person driving the trike is on the left of the photographer##1
 5. the person driving the car is the coach##1
 6. the fisherman is in the middle##1
 7. the musician is the person driving the tram##1
 8. the ranch-style house is on the right of the art-deco house##1
 9. the person driving the car is the ranch-style house##1
10. the writer is the palace house##1
11. the coach is on the right of the manager##1
12. the person driving the trike is on the left of the photographer##1
13. the victorian house is on the left of the futuristic house##1
14. the person driving the bus is on the left of the coach##1
15. the writer is on the right of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2       |    3     |     4      |    5     |    6    |     7      |
| Job           | dancer | photographer | musician | fisherman  | writer   | manager | coach      |
| Transport   | trike | ship        | tram    | subway     | jet-ski     | bus   | car        |
| House           | victorian   | futuristic       | craftsman    | tower | palace | art-deco   | ranch-style |

