.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-20::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, coffee, cola, fanta, iced-tea, sprite
There are 7 different nationalities: french, australian, italian, chinese, american, egyptian, polish
There 7 different types of food: apple, peach, tomato, kiwi, grapes, potato, asparagus
 1. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
 2. the person eating potato is in the middle##1
 3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is the french##1
 5. the egyptian is on the far right##1
 6. the person eating potato is the person drinking cola##1
 7. the person eating tomato is the egyptian##1
 8. the person eating kiwi is between the italian and the person eating tomato##2
 9. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the person eating peach##1
10. the chinese is in the middle##1
11. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person eating peach##1
12. the egyptian is on the right of the american##1
13. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
14. the australian is between the person eating asparagus and the polish##2
15. the person eating asparagus is the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |      4      |     5      |      6      |     7     |
| Beverage   | sprite  | iced-tea   | fanta   | cola        | coffee     | almond-milk | 7up       |
| Nationality      | french | australian | polish | chinese | italian  | american   | egyptian |
| Food        | asparagus   | peach     | apple     | potato      | grapes | kiwi    | tomato      |

 